body:
As you can see from the title, this is my second AMA. I thought since i'm starting to get more known on the server, but not to the point where everyone knows me. I'm starting up this AMA for those who want to know me better than they already do, and those who don't know me at all. I figured it's a fun way to connect with the community and get my name out there! 

Some info on me: 

Hi, my name is Jackson, i'm 14 and I play MC (obviously), LoL, and am planning on getting CS:GO. I play Soccer (Football) and Baketball and i'm in 9th Gr. to be specific. Check my profile for more details! :D
